

	To create a link to another site you can either:
		call the site using a dialup modem, leased line or LAN
			or
		accept calls from the site

&
Create a new link or modify an existing link
exec menu newlink.menu
List existing links
listlinks.sh; exec menu links.menu
Display link information
showlink.sh; exec menu links.menu
Remove a link
rmlnk.sh; exec menu links.menu
Return to main menu
exec menu config.menu
